    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Welcome Strategy Fans &amp; Playtesters!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We are currently in active development and looking for feedback on <strong>unit balance</strong> and <strong>drafting mechanics</strong>. If you love theory-crafting builds in games like <i>Backpack Battles</i>, <i>Teamfight Tactics</i>, or <i>Auto Chess</i>, we want your input to help shape Valefor 2.</p><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326570/extras/e9d7557bfb276286c86a06dbbb83c2b5.poster.avif?t=1769641848\" width=848 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326570/extras/e9d7557bfb276286c86a06dbbb83c2b5.webm?t=1769641848\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326570/extras/e9d7557bfb276286c86a06dbbb83c2b5.mp4?t=1769641848\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key features include:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Play at Your Pace:</strong> Strategic auto-battler matches with asynchronous PvP. No turn timers—make your move when you're ready.<br></li><li> <strong>Deep Drafting:</strong> React to opponents with evolving team compositions and synergies.<br></li><li> <strong>Economy Management:</strong> Manage resources to upgrade units, reroll recruits, and power up your board.<br></li><li> <strong>Crafting Strategy:</strong> Equipment crafting and item combinations that transform your champions' abilities.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326570/extras/1a7bcc0a05ed18417c68323f3f40f829.poster.avif?t=1769641848\" width=848 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326570/extras/1a7bcc0a05ed18417c68323f3f40f829.webm?t=1769641848\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326570/extras/1a7bcc0a05ed18417c68323f3f40f829.mp4?t=1769641848\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>A Note on Visuals:</strong><br><i>This is an early gameplay test focused on mechanics. Some assets you see are placeholders or legacy art. Our new visual style is currently in production and will be arriving in future updates!</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326570/extras/4f3b972b70afdd250cf7c6bb8b691af0.avif?t=1769641848\" width=1440 height=740 /></span>",
